Hsarat
Hsarat (Arabic: حصارات‎) (also spelled Hisarat, Hasrat, Hsarate, Ḩaşrāt, Hsârâte, Hsarale or Ḩişārāt)  is a village in the Jbeil District of the Mount Lebanon Governorate, Lebanon.
